item.title: Mission Statement
item.description: Hey guys! We’re all really excited about our first blog post. In this one, we’d like to elaborate on what OSDLabs stands to do and how you can be a part of it. For those of you who don’t know, Open Source Development Labs is an initiative to bring Open Source innovation to campus. We have always believed in sharing code and building better software. Period. This is what ‘Open Source’ fundamentally means.
